52 Week 2006-2007 DC Comics Renee Montoya FANEDIT bsg4you

THIS FANEDIT ONLY INCLUDES RENEE MONTOYA'S STORY FROM 52 WEEK

Do you like the DC Comics character Renee Montoya? Do you like the crime fighter The Question?

If yes, this 175 page FANEDIT of Renee Montoya's story from the 52 Week comic series should be very enjoyable. It tells the story of the previous Question, Charles "Charlie" Victor Szasz, reaching out to Renee who just had her partner killed, lost her job and girlfriend and is medicating herself with massive amounts of alcohol to numb her pain. Charlie and Renee embark on a world wide journey encountering alien technology, super-powered heroes and villains, cults, monasteries and new friends and foes. At the end, Renee has transformed herself and is ready to take on the crime fighting role of The Question.

This fanedit removes all the non-Renee story content and includes a custom cover and 21 custom pages. Plus, The Origin Of The Question and every 52 Week cover with Renee or The Question are included at the end.
